documentation.text:
base contract for consent contracts
 @title Consent Contract

create a new consent contract
 @param _contractID each contract has a unique contractID

get the contract represented in "json" string
 @return object as string

both parties need to sign the contract inorder to start the energy sharing
 proposer also needs to sign the contract because the consenter
 can modify the regulations before the contract is active

documentation.text:
proposer need to deposit the agreed price to the contract wallet
 {require} both parties need to sign the contract before
 {require} the msg.value needs to be the agreed price

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Nothing withdraw, consenter needs to send ETH first"

documentation.text:
withdraw the ethers balance from the contract to address of the consenter
 after withdraw the contract is active and running
 {require} ethers were deposited to the contract

params._contractID: each contract has a unique contractID

params._consenter: give consent about the energy data to the proposer
params._endEnergyData: end date of the energy date (epoche)
params._pricePerHour: price for 1h of energy data (in Wei)
params._proposer: creator of the contract (wants energy data from the consenter)
params._startEnergyData: start date of the energy date (epoche)
params._totalPrice: total price for all energy data (in Wei)

deposit().notice: proposer need to deposit the agreed price to the contract wallet {require} both parties need to sign the contract before {require} the msg.value needs to be the agreed price

getContractDetails().notice: get the contract represented in "json" string

getState().notice: returns the current state of the contract used for displaying status in the UI

signContract().notice: both parties need to sign the contract inorder to start the energy sharing proposer also needs to sign the contract because the consenter can modify the regulations before the contract is active

withdraw().notice: withdraw the ethers balance from the contract to address of the consenter after withdraw the contract is active and running {require} ethers were deposited to the contract
